Afropop singer, Davido has reacted to reports that music executive, Ubi Franklin is set to welcome his fourth child from a fourth woman any time soon. Davido took to Instagram to hail the music executive calling him ‘LEGEND’. Many people have wondered how the Triple MG music executive has been sleeping around with the women and impregnating them without using protection. He is reportedly expecting the baby with a businesswoman, Sandra Iheuwa. Just last month, Ubi welcomed his third child with his former staff, a South African lady, named Nicola Siyo. See Davido’s reaction below: Source